Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没睡啊  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加部团活动变得精神了是不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么拿着开罐器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12950元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差两万左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是买不起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…吃多了  好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样就算吃过三天的量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  你回来啦？那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  阿伸啊  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你该还我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我借你什么东西了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱…钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千元…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一万元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得被人请客吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却输掉了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉了约定不说  还输给了贫穷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她输一次比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让川添珠姬输一次比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对手不能是像我们这样大男人或男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要年龄相仿的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培养这样的才能很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么培养不培养啦  就我那水平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  部团活动只要玩的高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我自己能在这学校待到什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:05:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是常任教师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不好好做这个担当教师的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兼职两间学校吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要和另一间的剑道部比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过什么时候比还完全没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  要先找到第五名女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说回来  男生却只有我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山和岩佐的风评太差  男生都不太想加入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们现在都不来就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  男生有你们两个就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下来是小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别光休息  来练习咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你们怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑色小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…因为我的脚底很疼  所以不太想动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命练习的话  水泡也会结成茧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要输给疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天休息一下又不会死！人家是女孩子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种脚磨破也要继续的热血留给男生足够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家小都都长了一双美脚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你自己的脚底下不更是光光滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你有什么资格说别人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DVDBOX
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我不去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟姐姐说一声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小都都  这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校是禁止打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去朋友的店里临时帮帮忙而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当帮忙的话  有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得小都都打工怎么了  小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见  小珠向我开口说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…打工很辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会哦  只是帮忙看店而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你要不要试试看？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  但是那么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单  还能拿到不少零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子来劲啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就…试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在与风融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侧座摩托吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小珠  我们这就回去了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那店面的事情就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在后面做其它工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我在的话  客人就不太上门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会找小都来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多指教咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏小珠肯帮我补缺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  早上还好好的  现在却越来越疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真不该来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早点回去睡觉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  不要太勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我来载你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  段郎  你好温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  我是你的男朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已经足够了  段郎的脚够不到脚踏板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  你这份心简直就是特效药哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侧座摩托吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小珠  记得给家里打个电话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是回去晚了  家人会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白了  我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  爸爸说不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会晚回来？打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬去打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校没有禁止吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！我家珠姬学坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且会晚归？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行！就算以珠姬的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没拿竹剑的话就跟杂兵并没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为什么要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说零用钱的话  我每个月不都有给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想待在家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是对我有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬  打工的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  好好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是晚归的话  我去接你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬她终于长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想怎么突然就要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一周…就是我的生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本月的谚语  「とらぬ狸の皮算用」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（句意是捉摸着怎么卖还没有抓到的狸的皮。指对不切实际的事情抱有期待）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在摩托侧座放小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在摩托侧座放段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放哪一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想顺便去一家店看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前不是有间中古书店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那间完全没漫画的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你想去那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  现在那里新开了一家店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖可爱的小东西？我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就是那间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  店员就好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  选这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些汗是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份鼓动又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的钱由我暂时保管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的钱不够！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你偷了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被逮捕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,560元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收您1000元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找您440元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  袋子就不用了  我直接拿走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得说「谢谢您的惠顾」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要记得加上「欢迎下次再来」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎下四载来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打结了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让其他老师发现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说学校都禁止打工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不要因为害怕就跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工也是在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途跑是很没有责任的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…那是我还是高中生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始当点货的打工生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是和同级生的山本一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他突然和他女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:16.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本那混蛋  前几日难得见面却变得那么无可理喻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有后续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关机好了  现在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果像刚才那样又结巴了就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  如果客人不来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我只要打扫卫生  就不用说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:16:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪哦  刚才有谁在下「客人别上门」的诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道的话不过怎么样的对手都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要戴头盔拿起竹剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要洗澡  流了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要写功课  我得振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田虎侍先生吗  麻烦你盖章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  签名行么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈寄来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啥是啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙带菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡水就能恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加在拉面里吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙带菜  裙带菜  裙带菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间看电视上说裙带菜对身体很好  所以寄给你点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是吃方便食品和商店便当  磷酸摄取过量对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说裙带菜里面可是富含人体内因摄取磷酸而减少的镁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人生活营养跟不上  记得多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  对身体好就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没救啦！那老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是被电视广告拐走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后寄一大堆芝麻  可可亚  维生素片来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这些东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你干脆就不要买啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…最近都没回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是店里来强盗了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱拿出来！另外把可爱的东西都交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子火焰剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！Braver！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有竹剑我是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有什么可以代替的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮鞭？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多可以休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午你还有部团活动对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小都在活动结束后过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我提醒一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要拿去做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:22.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:27.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:34.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:55.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:23:02.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:10.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:20.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:25.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:32.38,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:35.38,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:40.38,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:48.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:22.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:27.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:34.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:55.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:23:02.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:10.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:20.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:25.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:32.38,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:35.38,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:40.38,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:48.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是东聪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话虽然我现在还完全没什么戏份
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:24:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是下周多少也有登场  记得为我加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  第九话将播出「小次郎和命运的分歧点」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东  这可要30秒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  预告要30秒吗？早点告诉我啦
